# UI Library — @erp/ui

## Import rule

**Always import from `@erp/ui`**, never from Radix UI or sub-packages directly in app code:

```tsx
// ✓ correct
import { Button, cn, ScrollArea, Tooltip, TooltipTrigger, TooltipContent } from @erp/ui";

// ✗ wrong — bypass the shared library
import * as Tooltip from "@radix-ui/react-tooltip";
```

## Available components

### Primitives
| Export | Use for |
|---|---|
| `Button` | All interactive buttons. Variants: `default`, `destructive`, `outline`, `secondary`, `ghost`, `link`. Sizes: `default`, `sm`, `lg`, `icon` |
| `Input` | Single-line text inputs |
| `Textarea` | Multi-line inputs |
| `Label` | Form labels (wraps Radix Label) |
| `Badge` | Status chips. Variants: `default`, `secondary`, `destructive`, `outline` |
| `Separator` | Horizontal/vertical dividers |

### Layout & overlay
| Export | Use for |
|---|---|
| `Card`, `CardHeader`, `CardTitle`, `CardDescription`, `CardContent`, `CardFooter` | Contained content blocks |
| `Dialog`, `DialogContent`, `DialogHeader`, `DialogFooter`, `DialogTitle`, `DialogDescription` | Modal dialogs |
| `AppModal` | Pre-built modal with save/cancel buttons and optional fullscreen toggle |
| `ScrollArea`, `ScrollBar` | Custom scrollable containers |
| `Collapsible`, `CollapsibleTrigger`, `CollapsibleContent` | Expand/collapse sections |
| `Tooltip`, `TooltipTrigger`, `TooltipContent`, `TooltipProvider` | Hover tooltips |
| `DropdownMenu`, `DropdownMenuTrigger`, `DropdownMenuContent`, `DropdownMenuItem`, `DropdownMenuLabel`, `DropdownMenuSeparator` | Dropdown menus |

### Form helpers
| Export | Use for |
|---|---|
| `FormField` | Wrapper: label + input + error + hint |
| `SearchInput` | Text input with clear button and search icon |
| `DateTimeField` | Date or datetime input (controlled by `includeTime` prop) |
| `LargeTextInput` | Textarea with min-height 160px |
| `TagsInput` | Inline tag input (Enter to add, Backspace to remove) |
| `MultiSelect` | Popover-based multi-select with checkboxes |

### Display / identity
| Export | Use for |
|---|---|
| `Avatar` | Initials-based avatar. Props: `name`, `size` (`sm`/`md`/`lg`) |
| `PageToolbar` | Action bar for list pages. See dedicated section below |

### Utilities
| Export | Use for |
|---|---|
| `cn(...classes)` | Merge Tailwind classes (clsx + tailwind-merge). Always use instead of manual string concat |
| `buttonVariants` | Apply button styles without the `<Button>` wrapper |

