## Icons

Always use `lucide-react` (already a dep of `@erp/ui` and both apps):

```tsx
import { Plus, Pencil, Trash2, Package, ChevronDown } from "lucide-react";

// Standard sizes
<Plus className="h-4 w-4" />        // in buttons, list items
<Package className="h-5 w-5" />     // in sidebar module rows
<ChevronDown className="h-3.5 w-3.5" />  // in accordion triggers
```

Never import icon sets other than lucide-react.

